---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import Header from "../components/Header.astro"
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro"
import BurgerMenu from "../components/BurgerMenu.astro"
import Perks from "../img/wine-subscription/perks.webp"
import Included2 from "../img/wine-subscription/included2.webp"
import Included1 from "../img/wine-subscription/included1.webp"
import Included3 from "../img/wine-subscription/included3.webp"
import Farmer from "../img/wine-subscription/farmer.webp"
import Grapes from "../img/wine-subscription/grapes.webp"
---
<Layout>
    <Header/>
<div class="px-body-padding-x lg:hidden pt-space-xl">
    <h2>Wine Subscriptions</h2>
    <p class="pt-space-s">The Great Wine Experience is delighted to offer convenient monthly wine club subscriptions of our top-quality range of hand-picked artisanal wines. 
    </p>
    <p class="py-space-m">Every month you'll receive a tasting box with 6 different wines carefully curated by our sommelier Natalie Noryd. In your tasting box, you will always find a wide range of wine styles guaranteeing something for every taste.</p>
    <p class="pb-space-l">Below you can read further about the benefits of a wine box subscriptions.</p>
</div>

<div class=" grid grid-cols-winesubscriptions-deluxe mb-space-s lg:hidden">
    <div class="deluxe">
        <h5 class="px-body-padding-x py-space-m">The Deluxe</h5>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-product-list px-body-padding-x py-space-m">
        <h6 class="pb-space-s">Six bottles for 695 DKK per month</h6>
        <p class="pb-space-l">A wide selection of quality wines, priced between 100-250 DKK per bottle</p>
        <a class="btn" href="">View box</a>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-cols-winesubscriptions-premium border-b-2 border-line-checkout pb-space-xl lg:hidden ">
    <div class="bg-product-list px-body-padding-x py-space-m">
        <h6 class="pb-space-s">Six bottles for 695 DKK per month</h6>
        <p class="pb-space-l">A wide selection of quality wines, priced between 100-250 DKK per bottle</p>
        <a class="btn" href="">View box</a>
    </div>

    <div class="premium">
        <h5 class="px-body-padding-x py-space-m">The Premium</h5>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="hidden lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:px-body-padding-x lg:gap-space-xl border-b-2 border-line-checkout pt-space-3xl">
    <div class="pr-space-3xl">
        <h2>Wine Subscriptions</h2>
        <p class="pt-space-l">The Great Wine Experience is delighted to offer convenient monthly wine club subscriptions of our top-quality range of hand-picked artisanal wines. 
        </p>
        <p class="py-space-m">Every month you'll receive a tasting box with 6 different wines carefully curated by our sommelier Natalie Noryd. In your tasting box, you will always find a wide range of wine styles guaranteeing something for every taste.</p>
        <p class="pb-space-l">Below you can read further about the benefits of a wine box subscriptions.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-deluxe gap-2 mb-space-m">
            <div class="deluxe">
                <h5 class="px-space-m py-space-m">The Deluxe</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-product-list px-space-m py-space-m">
                <h6 class="pb-space-s">Six bottles for 695 DKK per month</h6>
                <p class="pb-space-l">A wide selection of quality wines, priced between 100-250 DKK per bottle</p>
                <a class="btn" href="">View box</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-premium gap-2 mb-space-2xl">
            <div class="bg-product-list px-space-m py-space-m">
                <h6 class="pb-space-s">Six bottles for 695 DKK per month</h6>
                <p class="pb-space-l">A wide selection of quality wines, priced between 100-250 DKK per bottle</p>
                <a class="btn" href="">View box</a>
            </div>
            <div class="premium">
                <h5 class="px-space-m py-space-m">The Premium</h5>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<div class="md:hidden border-b-2 border-line-checkout">
    <div class="perks px-body-padding-x pt-space-xl pb-space-m">
        <p class="overlineText">Benefits</p>
        <h3>Prek up your palate!</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="px-body-padding-x">
        <div class="pt-space-xl flex flex-col gap-space-s">
            <h6>25% off + Free shipping</h6>
            <p>Get at least 25% off on each wine and free shipping across Denmark or you can choose to pick up your tasting box at our wine shop in Nordhavn.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-space-l flex flex-col gap-space-s">
            <h6>Tailor your subscription</h6>
            <p>Customize the selection of wines to your taste - a choice of all reds, all whites, or a mix. The selection also reflects the seasons, and can include rosés, sparkling or port wines.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-space-l flex flex-col gap-space-s pb-space-xl">
            <h6>Free to cancel or pause subscription</h6>
            <p>Your subscription is non-binding, you can choose to cancel or take a break as it suits you.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="hidden md:grid md:grid-cols-2 border-b-2 border-line-checkout">
    <div class="px-body-padding-x pt-space-3xl lg:pr-space-3xl">
        <div>
            <p class="overlineText">Benefits</p>
            <h3>Prek up your palate!</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-space-l flex flex-col gap-space-s">
            <h6>25% off + Free shipping</h6>
            <p>Get at least 25% off on each wine and free shipping across Denmark or you can choose to pick up your tasting box at our wine shop in Nordhavn.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-space-l flex flex-col gap-space-s">
            <h6>Tailor your subscription</h6>
            <p>Customize the selection of wines to your taste - a choice of all reds, all whites, or a mix. The selection also reflects the seasons, and can include rosés, sparkling or port wines.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-space-l flex flex-col gap-space-s pb-space-ll">
            <h6>Free to cancel or pause subscription</h6>
            <p>Your subscription is non-binding, you can choose to cancel or take a break as it suits you.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <img class="h-[100vh] w-full object-cover" src={Perks} alt="perks"/>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="md:hidden border-b-2 border-line-checkout">
    <h3 class="px-body-padding-x pt-space-xl pb-space-m">What's included</h3>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-included-top">
        <p class="px-body-padding-x">A typical Premium, or Deluxe Case contains one sparkling wine, two white wines and three red wines, the wines also change month-to-month. </p>
        <img class="h-[16rem] w-full object-cover" src={Included2} alt="included"/>
    </div>

    <p class="px-body-padding-x py-space-l">The selection of wines changes according to the season. In the summer you might find a refreshing rosé wine in your case and during the holidays a bottle of festive port.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-included-bottom">
        <img class="h-[24rem] w-full object-cover" src={Included1} alt="included"/>
        <p class="px-body-padding-x">Sommelier Natalie also carefully curates your selection to suit all occasions. Your shipment covers wines for all events so could include a fresh aperitif, a light everyday wine, or the perfect wine for your dinner party.</p>
    </div>

</div>

<div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-included hidden border-b-2 border-line-checkout">
    <div class="px-body-padding-x py-space-3xl">
        <h3 class="pb-space-s">What's included</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-space-m">
            <p>A typical Premium, or Deluxe Case contains one sparkling wine, two white wines and three red wines, the wines also change month-to-month. </p>
            <p>The selection of wines changes according to the season. In the summer you might find a refreshing rosé wine in your case and during the holidays a bottle of festive port.</p>
            <p>Sommelier Natalie also carefully curates your selection to suit all occasions. Your shipment covers wines for all events so could include a fresh aperitif, a light everyday wine, or the perfect wine for your dinner party.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 items-center gap-2">
        <img class="md:h-[24rem] lg:h-[20rem] w-full object-cover" src={Included1} alt="included"/>
        <img class="md:h-[24rem] lg:h-[20rem] w-full object-cover" src={Included2} alt="included"/>
        <img class="md:h-[24rem] lg:h-[20rem] w-full object-cover" src={Included3} alt="included"/>
    </div>
</div>

<div class=" md:hidden border-b-2 border-line-checkout">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2">
        <div class="px-body-padding-x pt-space-xl">
            <h3 class="pb-space-m">Winemakers</h3>
            <p>From grape to glass, winemaking is of the highest quality and fantastic taste is paramount.</p>
        </div>
        <img class="h-[16rem] w-full object-cover" src={Farmer} alt="farmer"/>
    </div>

    <div class="px-body-padding-x py-space-l flex flex-col gap-space-m">
        <p>We source all our wines from small to medium-sized traditional family wineries in legendary Old and New World wine regions. </p>
    
        <p>Each producer is dedicated to crafting wines free from unnecessary pesticides, chemicals and additives.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grapes">
        <h3 class="text-white px-body-padding-x pt-[16rem] pb-space-l">All wines are either organic, biodynamic, produced sustainably, or vegan.</h3>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="hidden md:grid md:grid-cols-winemakers border-b-2 border-line-checkout">

    <div class="col-span-2 px-body-padding-x pt-space-3xl flex flex-col gap-space-s pb-space-l">
        <h3>Winemakers</h3>
        <p>From grape to glass, winemaking is of the highest quality and fantastic taste is paramount.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row-span-2">
        <img class="h-[28rem] w-full object-cover" src={Farmer} alt="farmer"/>
    </div>

    <div class="row-span-2">
        <img class="md:h-[28rem] lg:h-[26rem] w-full object-cover" src={Grapes} alt="grapes"/>
    </div>

    <div class="px-body-padding-x flex flex-col gap-space-m pb-space-3xl">
        <p>We source all our wines from small to medium-sized traditional family wineries in legendary Old and New World wine regions. </p>

        <p>Each producer is dedicated to crafting wines free from unnecessary pesticides, chemicals and additives.</p>

        <p>All wines are either organic, biodynamic, produced sustainably, or vegan.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<Footer/>
    <BurgerMenu/>
</Layout>

<style>
    .deluxe{
    background-image: url("../img/wine-subscription/winebox1.webp");
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: cover;
 }

 .premium{
    background-image: url("../img/wine-subscription/winebox1.webp");
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: cover;
 }

 .perks{
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: 50% 47%;
    background-size: cover;
    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.373), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.373)), url("../img/wine-subscription/perks.webp");
 }

 .grapes{
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: cover;
    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.23), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.23)), url("../img/wine-subscription/grapes.webp");
 }

 a{
    border-bottom: black solid 2px;
 }


</style>